{"title":"Hottest picks","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"unholy-saint","title":"UNHOLY SAINT ♡","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32  WEARING M HOODIE.\r\n\r\n420 GSM\r\nPIPING WORK OVER SHOULDER, ARMS AND WAIST AREA\r\nPREMIUM 100% COTTON MATERIAL\r\nEMBROIDERY PRINT FRONT AND BACK (78,000+ embroidery stitches)\r\nBAGGY FIT [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS].\r\nCOMBED AND BIOWASHED.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStep into elevated streetwear with this 420 GSM super-premium sweatshirt, crafted for comfort, durability, and bold style. Made using combed and bio-washed fabric, it delivers a smooth, soft feel with long-lasting quality. The design features sleek piping work running across the shoulders, arms, and waist, adding a sharp, structured look. Front and back high-density embroidery make a strong statement, showcasing intricate detailing that stands out. With its relaxed fit, this sweatshirt blends effortless vibe with premium construction—perfect for everyday wear or standout street style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Machine wash the sweatshirt inside out with like colors.\r\n* Use cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\n* Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\n* Store the sweatshirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Sweatshirt with 420 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\n* Baggy fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\n* Unisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\n* Front pouch pocket for convenient storage and added warmth.\r\n* Soft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\r\n* Long sleeves and ribbed cuffs and hem provide a snug and stylish fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853858197658,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853858230426,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853858263194,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853858295962,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853858328730,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/B6CFEE9B-C671-41C1-9335-0E6FB2AFEC1D.png?v=1769958160"},{"product_id":"certified-lover-ltd-ed","title":"CERTIFIED LOVER","description":"\r\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\r\nEmbroidery work front\/back.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM black oversized T-shirt is crafted to offer a bold, streetwear-inspired aesthetic with premium details. Designed with a white cloth lining running from top to bottom, as well as from the front neck to the shoulder area, it brings a fresh touch to your look. The front features an embroidered logo, adding a touch of sophistication and an elevated vibe to the piece. On the back, the embroidered “Certified Lover” (that too in embroidery) print adds an extra layer of exclusivity. Perfect for those who appreciate luxury and street style, this T-shirt combines comfort, durability, and high-end craftsmanship.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407434906,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407467674,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407500442,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407533210,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881407598746,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407631514,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00022copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440426"},{"product_id":"code-9-flagged","title":"CODE-9 FLAGGED","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Fabric with Raglan Sleeves. Front \u0026amp; Back Print. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 260 GSM T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who like their style bold and unapologetic. Featuring classic raglan sleeves, it delivers enhanced comfort, mobility, and a distinct athletic-inspired silhouette. The front showcases the Drip Studios brand print with a clean, confident presence, while the back makes a powerful statement with the phrase “Are You Flagged and Certified Lover.” Crafted from high-quality French terry cotton, this tee offers durability, breathability, and all-day comfort. CODE 9 is made for individuals who wear their mindset as confidently as their style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and print longevity. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM fabric for a structured, premium feel. Raglan sleeves for improved comfort and a relaxed yet refined fit. Boxy, oversized silhouette suitable for both men and women. Unisex design crafted to complement diverse body types. Soft, breathable French terry cotton ensures lasting comfort and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407664282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407697050,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407729818,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407795354,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407828122,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00076copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440450"},{"product_id":"rules-breaker-black","title":"RULES BREAKER I - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Fabric. Oversized Fit with Raglan Sleeves. Front Embroidery \u0026amp; Back Silicone Print. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis oversized 240 GSM waffle T-shirt from Drip Studios is built for comfort with a refined edge. Designed with raglan sleeves for enhanced mobility and a relaxed drape, it delivers a super-comfy yet decent silhouette. The front features a clean embroidered “Rules Breaker” logo, keeping it minimal and premium, while the back makes a bold statement with a high-quality silicone print reading “Rules Breaker.” Crafted from combed and bio-washed cotton waffle fabric, this tee offers breathability, texture, and lasting softness—perfect for elevated everyday wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM waffle fabric for a textured, premium feel. Oversized fit for a relaxed and comfortable silhouette. Raglan sleeves for improved movement and fit. Front embroidered logo with back silicone print for durability and style. Unisex design suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408843930,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408876698,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408909466,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408942234,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881408975002,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881409007770,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00497copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440585"},{"product_id":"holy-flex","title":"HOLY FLEX","description":"\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M TEE.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e280 GSM premium French terry fabric for a substantial and durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit with full raglan sleeves for relaxed comfort and easy movement.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClassic black and white color blocking with a crisp white body and deep black sleeves.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLow-density front print featuring subtle script “Drip Studios” branding.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVertical “Drip Studios” screen print on sleeves for a bold yet minimal look.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImpactful Christ face graphic on the back with low-density print for a softer, artistic texture.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePiping work over the armhole area enhances structure and detailing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed finish for smooth texture and long-lasting quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the tee inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or fabric damage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCore Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTee with 280 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a premium, substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex article designed for versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable fabric ensures all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885005820058,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885005852826,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885005885594,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885005918362,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885005951130,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885005983898,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00348copy_11zon_1.jpg?v=1771440511"},{"product_id":"resilient","title":"RESILIENCE","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy-Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Piping Work \u0026amp; Embroidery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM boxy-fit T-shirt is designed for a strong, confident everyday statement with premium comfort at its core. Crafted from 100% French terry cotton, it offers a soft yet substantial feel with excellent breathability and durability. The design is elevated with refined piping work across the shoulders and front, adding depth and structure to the silhouette. Premium embroidery detailing on both the front and back enhances the overall craftsmanship, delivering a clean yet bold aesthetic. Finished with combed and bio-washed fabric, this tee ensures lasting softness, shape retention, and all-day wearability.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Do not iron directly on embroidery. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium, heavyweight feel. Boxy fit for a relaxed and modern silhouette. Piping work across shoulders and front for elevated detailing. Front and back embroidery for a refined, high-quality finish. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Combed and bio-washed fabric for superior softness, durability, and long-lasting comfort.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":47079340507290,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079340540058,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079340572826,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079340605594,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079340638362,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":47079340671130,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00511copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440397"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Premium Puff \u0026amp; Screen Print. Exclusive Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is crafted to combine premium comfort with bold, statement-driven design. Built from heavyweight French terry cotton, the fabric delivers a smooth, structured feel while remaining breathable and durable for all-day wear. Designed as an exclusive limited-edition release, the front features the striking \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in a combination of premium puff and screen printing for layered texture and depth. The back carries the signature \u003cstrong\u003e09\u003c\/strong\u003e brand number in the same high-quality print finish, creating a cohesive, standout identity from every angle. Combed and bio-washed for long-lasting softness and shape retention, this tee is made for those who move with confidence and presence.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain print texture and fabric quality. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium heavyweight structure. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for everyday statement wear. Front “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” artwork in premium puff and screen print combination. Back brand number 09 executed in matching high-quality print finish. Exclusive limited-edition design for elevated street presence. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500129829018,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500129861786,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500129894554,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47500129960090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47500129992858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687033159834,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772289837"},{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-dor-saint","title":"D'OR SAINT - Ltd. Ed.","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Cropped Ringer Design. Embroidered Front Detail. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Limited Edition (100 Pieces). Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis exclusive 240 GSM cropped ringer T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted to deliver a refined balance of vintage inspiration and modern luxury. Designed with signature contrast ringer trims on the neckline and sleeves, it features a clean cropped silhouette with a relaxed waist that offers effortless structure and comfort. The front is elevated with a finely embroidered detail that adds a subtle yet premium statement without overpowering the minimal aesthetic. Made from high-grade combed and bio-washed cotton, the fabric feels exceptionally soft, breathable, and durable for everyday wear. Strictly limited to only 100 pieces, this piece is designed for those who appreciate exclusivity, precision, and timeless streetwear luxury.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"99\" data-start=\"60\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and preserve the embroidery. Avoid harsh detergents or bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and embroidery finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric delivering a structured yet comfortable feel. Cropped ringer silhouette with contrast neckline and sleeve trims for a timeless aesthetic. Finely embroidered front detail adding a subtle luxury statement. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for balanced structure and movement. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish for enhanced softness and long-term durability. Exclusively limited to only 100 pieces.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47631552643226,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47631552675994,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47631552708762,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47631552741530,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/Copy_of_DSC00085_copy.jpg_11zon_1.webp?v=1773674828"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty-ii","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY II","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Heavyweight Fabric. High-Detail Puff Print Front \u0026amp; Back. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Exclusive YRM Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM premium T-shirt from the exclusive YRM limited-edition collection is designed to make a bold, unmistakable statement. Crafted from heavyweight fabric, it offers a structured yet breathable feel that delivers all-day comfort with a strong streetwear presence. The front and back feature intricately detailed \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in high-definition puff print, creating a striking raised texture that adds depth, dimension, and a premium visual impact. Designed for those who stand out effortlessly, this piece blends luxury aesthetics with everyday wearability. Combed and bio-washed for superior softness and long-lasting durability, it maintains its shape and finish over time while elevating your wardrobe with a powerful identity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric quality and puff print detailing. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM premium heavyweight fabric for a structured, high-end feel. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for statement streetwear. High-detail “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” puff print on both front and back for elevated texture and depth. Exclusive YRM limited-edition release for a distinctive look. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47682205384858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47682205417626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47682205450394,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47682205483162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47682205515930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687032373402,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00325_copy.webp?v=1774686690"}],"url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/collections\/hottest-picks.oembed","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}